sequenceDiagram
    actor Operator
    participant Agent
    participant Generator as Sample Generator
    participant Outbound as Email Out
    actor Target
    participant Inbound as Email In

    Operator->>Agent: approve pitch target
    Agent->>Generator: generate 4-min sample
    Generator-->>Agent: sample mp3 and URL
    Agent->>Outbound: send SAMPLE email
    Outbound->>Target: delivered

    alt reply yes
        Target->>Inbound: reply
        Inbound->>Agent: intent YES
        Agent->>Outbound: send CHECKOUT email
    else reply no or unsubscribe
        Target->>Inbound: reply
        Inbound->>Agent: intent NO
        Agent->>Agent: add to suppression list
    else silence 7 days
        Agent->>Outbound: optional single nudge
    else silence 14 days
        Agent->>Agent: permanent silence
    end
